rly flags (exam_crunch, part_time_job, house_party) also carry min_days_since 10-14 so nothing from this batch lands inside the onboarding week. No weight above 0.35, everything either cooldown-paced, one-shot-flagged, or clears its own trigger -- no unpaced loops. Contacts: all six threads reused from the registry (coach_hs, hs_friend, family_mom, family_dad x2 arcs, family_kid unused here), ZERO registry change. No new SubjectField/ConsequenceKind/schema anywhere -- pure content.",
